    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，管理员添加产品后从草稿变为可用状态。然后客户可以加入购物车，这个状态叫InCart。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Draft",
        "Available",
        "InCart",
        "Admin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把这几个核心状态连起来：草稿→可用→购物车。购物车应该能退回可用状态吧，比如客户删除商品？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InCart",
        "Available"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，购物车删除回到可用。另外购物车可以下单变成已预留Reserved，预留后支付成功就变成已售出Sold。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InCart",
        "Reserved",
        "Sold"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "售出之后有退货流程吗？还有，管理员能不能在任何阶段直接删除商品？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sold",
        "Removed",
        "Admin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
